    "Quotations from educators and parents support these suggestions.",
    "For instance, educator 1 stated, \"Cultural sensitivity is important when designing interventions for children with autism, particularly for those from diverse backgrounds.",
    "We need to ensure that the interventions are culturally relevant and take into account the unique needs and experiences of each child. \"",
    "Similarly, parent 6 stated, \"As a parent of a child with autism who comes from a different cultural background, I appreciate interventions that take into account my child's unique needs and experiences.",
    "It's important to have interventions that are culturally sensitive and relevant. \""
